<br>
On top of Hannibal, Yakut's main steed, was Glory and Ariel was in Tanna's arms. The Shamaness's horse Clarice was actually supposed to be Tanna's horse but T didn't like riding by herself. (Goddesses! Go figure! hehee)<br>
<br>
They group walked futher into the Valley passing the Vineyards that Yakut had planted by her own hands and walking down the Tanais River side to the Village.<br>
<br>
The Peace Seeker came upon the Gates to the Village of Tanais River Valley and entered with a smile. She lead her steeds to the stable and settle them in, leaving the cart outside tied to a hitching post.<br>
<br>
Yakut then moved to Raven's Hut and knocked on the door.<br>
<br>
&quot;Ravey? You in there?&quot; <p>§-:¦:-§ Yakut §-:¦:-§ <BR>
~Northern Amazon Queen of Tanais River Valley~<BR>
