When they all started heading back,she made for sure she got to walk instead of ride on the horse.As she walked she had a light skip in her steps, and was watching Raven. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=amazonprincessraven>Amazon Princess Raven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 42<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(8/20/02 8:04:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=49.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> .................</span><hr size=1> Raven turned back at little Glory and paused. She forced a smile and then sat down at the empty log looking at the plain fireplace that sat in the middle of the village.<br>
<br>
She then paused looking down to the blankness of the fireplace and her wrists gently reached out causing a spark to set and a small fire to blaze.<br>
<br>
She took one more glance back to Glory and paused wondering what the child was thinking of. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugloryoftrv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Glory of TRV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(8/21/02 2:55:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=49.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Sister,sister</span><hr size=1> Glory skipped over to Raven and sat down beside her.<br>
