Christanna watched and listened... and as Yakut went off to start unpacking, she made her way to the fire where Raven sat with Glory and Ariel. She figured she'd at least try to do something before going and helping Yakut.<br>
<br>
Kneeling down before Raven, she took both of her hands and kissed the inside of each wrist over the marks, then folded Raven's hands over her chest. &quot;Embrace it... we all have a dark side,&quot; she whispered softly, and then before a reaction could be given she stood and quickly went to their hut, walking up behind Yakut and putting her arms around her. &quot;Guess who?&quot; she said, nuzzling against her neck from behind. <p><html> <center> <font face="vivaldi" size="+1" color="#ffc0cb"> ~ Christanna : Amazon Goddess of Shamanism ~ <br> Proud wife to Yakut  and mother to Yakut's children</font> </center> </html></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showMessageRange?topicID=49.topic&start=21&stop=23>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showPrevMessage?topicID=49.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showNextMessage?topicID=49.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=49.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/rust/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.emailToFriend?topicID=49.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.threadControl?topicID=49.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/rust/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=49.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=ht